                <div style="background: #f8fafc; padding: 1rem; border-radius: var(--radius); margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                    <strong>Example:</strong><br>
                    <code>GET /api/nodes/2/5001/100/changes?noflags=1&nophone=1</code>
